      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">論語 4.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Analects I.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「里仁爲美。擇不處仁，焉得知？」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "It is virtuous manners which constitute the excellence of a neighborhood. If a man in selecting a residence, do not fix on one where such prevail, how can he be wise?"</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="lunyu__book-04-liren__002__zhwikisource-20260529__legge-cc-v1-1893">
      <prop type="x-work-id">lunyu</prop>
