      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">論語 4.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Analects III.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「惟仁者能好人，能惡人。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "It is only the (truly) virtuous man, who can love, or who can hate, others."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="lunyu__book-04-liren__004__zhwikisource-20260529__legge-cc-v1-1893">
      <prop type="x-work-id">lunyu</prop>
