      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Analects VIII.8</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「朝聞道，夕死可矣！」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "If a man in the morning hear the right way, he may die in the evening without regret."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
