      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Analects IX.9</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「士志於道，而恥惡衣惡食者，未足與議也！」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "A scholar, whose mind is set on truth, and who is ashamed of bad clothes and bad food, is not fit to be discoursed with."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
