      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「君子之於天下也，無適也，無莫也，義之與比。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "The superior man, in the world, does not set his mind either for anything, or against anything; what is right he will follow."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
