      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「君子懷德，小人懷土；君子懷刑，小人懷惠。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "The superior man thinks of virtue; the small man thinks of comfort. The superior man thinks of the sanctions of law; the small man thinks of favours which he may receive."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
