      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「能以禮讓爲國乎，何有？不能以禮讓爲國，如禮何？」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "If a prince is able to govern his kingdom with the complaisance proper to the rules of propriety, what difficulty will he have? If he cannot govern it with that complaisance, what has he to do with the rules of propriety?"</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
