      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "A man should say, I am not concerned that I have no place, I am concerned how I may fit myself for one. I am not concerned that I am not known, I seek to be worthy to be known."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="lunyu__book-04-liren__015__zhwikisource-20260529__legge-cc-v1-1893">
