      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「君子喻於義，小人喻於利。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "The mind of the superior man is conversant with righteousness; the mind of the mean man is conversant with gain."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
