      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「事父母幾諫；見志不從，又敬而不違，勞而不怨。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "In serving his parents, a son may remonstrate with them, but gently; when he sees that they do not incline to follow his advice, he shows an increased degree of reverence, but does not abandon his purpose; and should they punish him, he does not allow himself to murmur."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
