      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">論語 4.19</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Analects XIX.19</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「父母在，不遠遊；遊必有方。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "While his parents are alive, the son may not go abroad to a distance. If he does go abroad, he must have a fixed place to which he goes."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
