      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「三年無改於父之道，可謂孝矣。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "If the son for three years does not alter from the way of his father, he may be called filial."</seg>
      </tuv>
