      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「父母之年，不可不知也。一則以喜，一則以懼。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "The years of parents may by no means not be kept in the memory, as an occasion at once for joy and for fear."</seg>
      </tuv>
