        <seg>子曰：「古者言之不出，恥躬之不逮也。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "The reason why the ancients did not readily give utterance to their words, was that they feared lest their actions should not come up to them."</seg>
      </tuv>
